      <h1>How Video Builds Thought Leadership for Prospects</h1>
      <p class="lead">Build brand credibility with thought leadership videos. See how Viven's video production helps you attract qualified prospects.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>January 20, 2025</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 24, 2025</span></p>
